---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import { SITE } from '../../lib/site';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How Psychedelic Retreats Australia collects, uses, and protects personal information.">
  <Breadcrumbs items={[{ name: 'Privacy Policy', path: '/privacy/' }]} />

  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 pb-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl font-medium text-forest-900 sm:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-charcoal-soft">
      {/* TODO-ADAM: have this policy reviewed against the Australian Privacy Act 1988 (APPs) before this page goes live — this is a compliant-style draft, not legal advice, and doesn't yet reference a specific ABN/entity. */}
      Last updated: 19 July 2026 (draft)
    </p>

    <div class="prose-article mt-8">
      <h2>What we collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Enquiry and claim forms:</strong> name, email, and message content you submit via our enquiry or operator-claim forms.</li>
        <li><strong>Newsletter signup:</strong> your email address, via our newsletter provider (MailerLite).</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> aggregated, privacy-preserving website analytics via Cloudflare Web Analytics, which does not use cookies or track individuals across sites.</li>
        <li><strong>Anti-spam verification:</strong> Cloudflare Turnstile may process limited technical data (such as your IP address) to verify form submissions aren't automated.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How we use it</h2>
      <p>
        We use enquiry/claim form submissions to respond to you and, where relevant, to pass your enquiry to the
        listed operator. We use your email for newsletter signups only to send the content you signed up for. We
        do not sell your personal information.
      </p>

      <h2>Where it's stored</h2>
      <p>
        Form submissions are processed via Cloudflare Pages Functions and may be logged to a Cloudflare KV
        namespace and/or emailed to us for record-keeping. Newsletter data is held by our newsletter provider,
        MailerLite, under its own privacy policy.
      </p>

      <h2>Third parties</h2>
      <p>
        We use Cloudflare (hosting, forms, analytics, anti-spam), MailerLite (newsletter), and an email-sending
        provider (Resend or MailChannels) to operate this site — each processes limited data as described above,
        under their own privacy policies.
      </p>

      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <p>
        You can ask us to access, correct, or delete personal information we hold about you, or unsubscribe from
        our newsletter at any time via the link in any email. <a href="/contact/">Contact us</a> to make a request.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This site does not use tracking or advertising cookies. Any cookies used are strictly functional (for
        example, Cloudflare Turnstile's anti-spam verification).
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time; the "last updated" date above reflects the most recent revision.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Privacy questions or requests: <a href={`mailto:${SITE.contactEmail}`}>{SITE.contactEmail}</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
